No one said to powerlevel to 65. It's just that the exp is so good in PoP that you won't even notice you are leveling like crazy. Even just casually playing will net you 65 within 2-3 weeks if you don't go for aa. You can slowly progress if you want. But that's not what people are doing here. They are stopping completly from leveling.<br>
<br>
Not leveling would be more like getting to level 8-2 and never going further because you don't want to lose the chance of having to do the hardest jump in the game taken away from you. Sure you can stay there if you want, but you aren't progressing.<br>
<br>
