iscovered some soloing spots in PoD where I can get 3% AA per kill and kill at a decent rate.  This is when I'm level 61 and casting lots of air pets and FoT.  Last night I got 40% of an AA in an hour and a half.  Not bad for level 61 mage soloing with barely any FT and no rune items.  I might be able to speed it up with some tactics too.<br>
